description: The USB2HABM6IN USB to Mini USB Cable offers a 4-pin USB (A) male connector, as well as a 5-pin Mini USB (B) male connector, providing a high quality replacement for connecting your digital camera (Canon, Sony, Hewlett Packard) to a host computer, or maximizing the file transfer performance of your Mini-USB-equipped MP3 player, PDA or digital camcorder. Expertly designed and constructed of only top quality materials, this 6in USB/Mini USB cable is more than suitable for pure digital data transfers and sharp, natural images and sounds with support for high-speed USB 2.0 data transfer rates of up to 480Mbps.To ensure maximum reliability and performance, this cable is backed by Lifetime Warranty.
title: StarTech.com USB2HABM6IN 6-Inch Mini USB 2.0 Cable - A to Mini B
